Jack Wilshere and Luke Shaw were both subbed with cramp, but should be fit to face Honduras at the same stadium on Saturday.

England will be without Sterling, suspended for one game after he was sent off for a 79th-minute challenge on Manchester United winger Antonio Valencia, who retaliated and was also red-carded.

